thread.title_full: HiFX Australia reviewed by Roger Canton

author: Roger Canton
title: Roger Canton
text:
First time user - moved from OFX due to better rate and sponsorship of school rowing club. Happy so far.
Found getting an account opened relatively straight forward. Had expected to need to provide more paperwork. As long as competitive will keep using for monthly transfers
